[{"url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/pulls/1","id":3461442034,"node_id":"PR_kwDORxDd1s7OUWny","html_url":"https://github.com/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/pull/1","diff_url":"https://github.com/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/pull/1.diff","patch_url":"https://github.com/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/pull/1.patch","issue_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/issues/1","number":1,"state":"closed","locked":false,"title":"Add Gruvbox to theme switcher dropdown","user":{"login":"n8behavior","id":692218,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY5MjIxOA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/692218?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior","html_url":"https://github.com/n8behavior","followers_url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior/followers","following_url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior/following{/other_user}","gists_url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior/gists{/gist_id}","starred_url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior/starred{/owner}{/repo}","subscriptions_url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior/subscriptions","organizations_url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior/orgs","repos_url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior/repos","events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior/events{/privacy}","received_events_url":"https://api.github.com/users/n8behavior/received_events","type":"User","user_view_type":"public","site_admin":false},"body":"## Summary\n\n- Added `.gruvbox` to the CSS selector in `variables.css` so the theme applies when selected by name\n- Added a custom `index.hbs` template (based on mdBook 0.5.2 default) with a \"Gruvbox\" button in the theme switcher list\n- Updated `main.rs` to install `index.hbs` and set `default-theme`/`preferred-dark-theme` to `\"gruvbox\"` in `book.toml`\n\n## Problem\n\nAfter running `mdbook-gruvbox install`, the theme works but \"Gruvbox\" doesn't appear in the theme switcher dropdown — only the built-in themes (Light, Rust, Coal, Navy, Ayu) are listed. Since the CSS overrides all of them, every option looks the same and there's no indication the user is on a custom theme.\n\n## How it works\n\nmdBook's theme switcher JS dynamically discovers themes from `<button class=\"theme\">` elements in the HTML. By providing a custom `index.hbs` with a Gruvbox button (`id=\"mdbook-theme-gruvbox\"`), the JS picks it up automatically — no JS changes needed. The `.gruvbox` CSS selector ensures the variables apply when the `<html>` element gets `class=\"gruvbox\"`.\n\n## Test plan\n\n- [ ] `cargo build` compiles clean\n- [ ] `mdbook-gruvbox install` on a fresh mdBook project writes `index.hbs` to the theme dir\n- [ ] `mdbook build` produces a book with \"Gruvbox\" in the theme dropdown\n- [ ] Selecting \"Gruvbox\" from the dropdown applies the gruvbox colors\n- [ ] Built-in themes still apply gruvbox colors (existing behavior preserved)","created_at":"2026-03-28T22:15:38Z","updated_at":"2026-03-28T22:51:48Z","closed_at":"2026-03-28T22:51:48Z","merged_at":"2026-03-28T22:51:48Z","merge_commit_sha":"9356ef9c02047960c05fd2e0a7ccff3aa92d90bd","assignees":[],"requested_reviewers":[],"requested_teams":[],"labels":[],"milestone":null,"draft":false,"commits_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/pulls/1/commits","review_comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/pulls/1/comments","review_comment_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/pulls/comments{/number}","comments_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/issues/1/comments","statuses_url":"https://api.github.com/repos/bfowle/mdbook-gruvbox/statuses/5fe37740c4d56d5a51bc5634f678e75c798bfb36","head":{"label":"n8behavior:add-gruvbox-to-theme-switcher","ref":"add-gruvbox-to-theme-switcher","sha":"5fe37740c4d56d5a51bc5634f678e75c798bfb36","user":{"login":"n8behavior","id":692218,"node_id":"MDQ6VXNlcjY5MjIxOA==","avatar_url":"https://avatars.githubusercontent.com/u/692218?v=4","gravatar_id":"","url":"htt